<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>진주커Pick</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/public/components/gifticon_upload.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/public/components/gifticon_lists.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet"  type="text/css" href="/public/header.css">
        
    </head>
    <body>
        <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a064522756.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <label id="bookmark-label"><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
            <input type="button" value="" class="bookmark-btt">
        </label>
        <div class="logo_back">
            <div class="side_menu">
                <section class="side_menu_container">
                    <ul class="bookmark-lists">
                        <li class="bookmark"><a href="/main">
                            <div id="main_home"> 진주커Pick</div>
                        </a></li>
                        <hr>
                        <li class="bookmark"><a href="/login">
                            <div class="bookmark-list"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-user" id="login"></i> 로그인</div>
                        </a></li>
                        <li class="bookmark"><a href="/gifticon_upload">
                            <div class="bookmark-list"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift" id="gifticon"></i> 기프티콘</div>
                        </a></li>
                        <li class="bookmark"><a href="/community">
                            <div class="bookmark-list"><i class="fa-solid fa-message" id="commu"></i> 커뮤니티</div>
                        </a></li>
                    
                    </ul>
                    <div class="info"><hr>경상국립대학교 얼죽아
                        <div id="info_1">수학과&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;강수연<br>정보통계학과&emsp;정인영<br>정보통계학과&emsp;정혜주<br>컴퓨터과학과&emsp;서혜원<br>컴퓨터과학과&emsp;이도현<hr></div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <script src="/public/index.js"></script>
            <div class="main_logo" style="text-align: center;"> 
                <img src="/public/static/jinju.textlogo.png" height= "110" alt="로고">
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="upload_section">
            <form id="myForm" method="post">
                <div class="fileInput">
                    <label for="gifticonImg" id="gifticonImgLabel">사진 불러오기</label>
                    <span>FILE NAME: </span><span id="fileName">&nbsp;</span>
                </div>
                <input type="file" id="gifticonImg" name="gifticonImg" accept="image/*" aria-required="true" required oninvalid="this.setCustomValidity('기프티콘 이미지를 선택해주세요.')" oninput="this.setCustomValidity('')">
                <table id="inputContainer">
                    <tr>
                        <td><label>카페명</td>
                        <td><input type="text" id="cafeName" name="cafeName" required oninvalid="this.setCustomValidity('카페명을 입력해주세요.')" oninput="this.setCustomValidity('')"></label><br></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><label>유효기간</td>
                        <td><input type="date" id="expirationDate" name="expirationDate" required oninvalid="this.setCustomValidity('유효기간을 선택해주세요.')" oninput="this.setCustomValidity('')"></label><br></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <input type="reset" id="reset_btn" value="초기화" onclick="document.getElementById('fileName').textContent = '&nbsp;'">
                <input type="submit" id="upload_btn" value="기프티콘 등록">
            </form>
            
            <article>
                <div class="check_section">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="ch_all" id="ch_all">
                    <label for="ch_all">전체선택 | </label>
                </div>
                <button class="del_btn" id="del_btn">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="gifticon_lists" id="gifticon_lists">
                </div>
            </article>

        </section>
        <script src="/public/gifticon_upload.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>